scores.comment: It is quiet here, I find it to be a really nice studying environment.
Sometimes it is so quiet, I feel like I might be disrupting others.
I'm an introvert so love that it's so quiet I'm never hassled by other people.
I hang out here with my work pals in total silence. It's bliss. We get a lot done here.
I get so much done here because none of my co-workers dare interrupt me.
It's alright if you are happy to work quietly and IM your friends. Can't talk though, it's so quiet!
Great vibe and a happening little cafe. Sometimes noisy, but never too loud.
I like it here and the music is great but sometimes it might be a little hard to concerntrate on you have some tricky concepts to cover..
They keep on calling me Gary. My name is Jerry.
Friendly staff and there's often someone to talk to if you feel like taking a break from the task at hand.
Great place to have a quick meeting but the atmosphere might be a little too casual to get a good amount of co-working done.
Found it hard to focus on work with others, but great place for a quick catch up with collegues before continuing the day's tasks.
The wi-fi was a little patchy and I had to resort to using my own connection at times.
Very funny wi-fi password.
There was a lot of grime on the power point, I avoided it.
Had to look around for a power point but there are a few about.
No troubles here!
Small bump and narrow doorway but staff were very accomodating when I arrived in my wheelchair.
Some traffic noise from the streets nearby, but still a peaceful outdoor area.
A nice quiet place to enjoy the sunshine.
A nice open place where you can meet other workers without worrying if you might be disturbing someone.
Can be a little noisy at times with other groups and families. Luckily it is a large open area and you can find your own space..
Don't have to worry about interrupting the quiet enjoyment of others, great spot for a client meeting in the sun.
Great place to have a chat with other workers out in the open air.
No internet available here but plenty of reception for mobile broadband.
Great reception for mobile broadband out here in the open.
You can find outlets here and there if yo have a thirsty laptop.
Got an outlet just in time to charge for that important call.
Great amount of open space that is wheelchair accessible
I can get to most areas with no trouble, but it would be great id there was more access to the tiered seating areas.
